    "date": "2021-12-17T16:11:03Z",
    "text": "Aiding Afghan Allies Act\n\nThis bill allows a tax credit, up to $300 in a taxable year, for charitable contributions made to evacuate individuals from Afghanistan who are U.S. citizens or lawful permanent residents or who are Afghan citizens or nationals who have submitted a petition for special immigrant status.\n\nThe period for making such contributions begins on August 14, 2021, and ends on September 30, 2022."
